  "body": "# Ethereum Core Devs Meeting 100 (!!) Agenda\r\n\r\n-   Meeting Date/Time:  **Friday 13 November 2020, [14:00 UTC](https://savvytime.com/converter/utc-to-germany-berlin-united-kingdom-london-ny-new-york-city-ca-san-francisco-china-shanghai-japan-tokyo-australia-sydney/nov-13-2020/2pm)**. \r\n    - _Daylight savings will have happened in North America, double check the time!_ \r\n-   Meeting Duration 1.5 hours\r\n-   YouTube Live Stream: https://youtu.be/5-614J9qNvY\r\n\r\n# Agenda\r\n\r\n1. YOLOv3 & Berlin client updates \r\n    - [YOLOv3 spec](https://github.com/ethereum/eth1.0-specs/blob/master/client-integration-testnets/YOLOv3.md)\r\n        - EIP-2718 clarification & interactions with 2930\r\n    - Final go/no-go for Berlin EIPs\r\n1. Network upgrade process update \r\n1. Other EIPs \r\n    - EIP-2938 (Account Abstraction) \r\n    - EIP-2666\r\n    - BLS12-381 \r\n1. Responsible disclosure / Geth bug \r\n\r\nNext call: November 27, 2020 14:00 UTC",
